{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act46side", "eventName": "雪山降臨1101", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "OS-3", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "雪灌木中", "storyInfo": "維多利亞大使與菈塔托絲會面，表達了單獨與布朗陶家合作的意願。在希瓦艾什與佩爾羅契的領地內分別發生了針對家主的刺殺。聖巡儀式中的恩雅遭遇刺客襲擊，危難之際被一位小獵手救下。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g8_nobleroom", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_278_1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_278_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "菈塔托絲大人，關於前天三家討論的事，我家大人還有話想和您說。", "name": "佩爾羅契信使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_278_1#1$1"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "佩爾羅契家對那些外來者的態度一貫是堅定的，對於那些沒有信仰的人，再怎麼警惕都不為過。", "name": "佩爾羅契信使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_278_1#1$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "何況現在聖女出巡，謝拉格的政務暫時分歸三家各自處理，這個時候我們更要多留一個心眼。", "name": "佩爾羅契信使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_278_1#1$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們大人並不是覺得恩希歐迪斯是個壞人，但是希瓦艾什家確實和維多利亞人走得太近了，誰也不確定他還會有什麼別的心思。", "name": "佩爾羅契信使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_278_1#1$1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大人他相信您是尊重謝拉格傳統的人，所以願意和您溝通。要是您還有什麼想法，我家大人也樂意和您當面聊聊。", "name": "佩爾羅契信使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_278_1#1$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……都說完了？", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，看在你這麼坦誠的份上，也替我原話轉告阿克托斯。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不知道阿克托斯是不是還因為天災發生在佩爾羅契的領地而耿耿於懷，我也不在乎。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是該討論的問題上次開會已經有結論了，沒有蔓珠院的指示，我們哪一家都不該輕舉妄動。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在聖女大人不在，我們各自照顧好自家的事，不要多生事端，就是對謝拉格最好的方式。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就這樣，送客。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g8_nobleroom", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來，這樣的麻煩在哪裡都躲不過。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#2$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓您見笑了，不過不必擔憂，只是一些小麻煩。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是讓我們回到正題上吧——關於維多利亞幾個高級服裝品牌和布朗陶家的長期合作……", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不……不不，尊敬的布朗陶夫人，我並不覺得這是一個可以忽視的問題。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果謝拉格的人們普遍對維多利亞懷有這樣的敵意，我們又該如何相信我們之間的合作能夠長久呢？", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們三大家族之間時有分歧，但是從來沒有別人可以代表布朗陶家的態度，這一點您可以放心。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三大家族的矛盾……哈哈，身為一個維多利亞人，這樣的局面也並不難理解。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#2$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "留在謝拉格的這段時間，我一直試圖瞭解這個國家，這裡的文化陌生，但是有趣。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#2$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在我看來，雖然謝拉格團結在對耶拉岡德的信仰之下，但是同樣的教義，似乎對不同的家族產生了截然不同的指導意義。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#2$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "佩爾羅契家族勇敢、希瓦艾什家族精明，至於布朗陶家……抱歉，我很難用單一的詞語表示讚賞。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#2$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果一定要說的話，我認為布朗陶家是“高尚且值得信賴的”。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#2$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……也真難為你們還要做這樣的功課。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#4$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，充分的瞭解是合作的前提。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "公爵大人十分看重與謝拉格的合作，而她也一直在尋找一位可靠的、能夠代表謝拉格的合作對象。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能夠代表謝拉格的合作對象？難道是公爵大人和喀蘭貿易的合作不愉快了？", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#5$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩希歐迪斯先生是一位無比聰明的商人，但這也是他的缺點。在他的生意場中，他絕對不允許出現除他以外的贏家。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "身為他的鄰居，我想您應該很清楚這一點。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵……還真是精準的概括。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "問題就在這裡，三大家族名義上是耶拉岡德平等的子民，可是在我一個純粹的旁觀者眼中，卻完全不這樣覺得。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恕我直言，就連我這個外人都看得出來，這場天災當中，您的家族與佩爾羅契家族幾乎無法做出任何有效決策。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希瓦艾什家的喀蘭貿易不僅壟斷了幾乎所有謝拉格的外貿生意，更是在政治層面主導了謝拉格的所有對外交流。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而理論上謝拉格真正的掌權者，聖女大人——也就是恩希歐迪斯先生的胞妹，她似乎對這樣的現狀沒有任何意見。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "注意你的言詞，先生。不要用你的偏見揣測謝拉格聖女的虔誠，這是極度的不敬。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#5$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，抱歉，如果我的坦誠冒犯了您，我為此道歉。請相信我絕對沒有惡意。如我剛才所說，這一切都只是一個外來者觀察到的現象。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了，就請直接說明吧——您到底有什麼提議？", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#5$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很簡單，維多利亞在尋求一種友好且平等、真正互利互惠的合作。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#2$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不只有某一方獲利，也不受限於狹隘的民族觀念。展開有效而長遠的合作。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#2$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而布朗陶家族以及您個人，也是受到公爵閣下青睞的，我出現在這裡即是證明。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#2$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "布朗陶家不會認為任何外人的看法具有價值。你們的承諾，恰好證明維多利亞的立場飄忽不定。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果在你們眼中布朗陶不過是另一個更好操縱的希瓦艾什，那就大錯特錯了。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不不，菈塔托絲大人，完全不。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維多利亞並非青睞順從者，也不圖他人攀附，而是做正確的事。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希瓦艾什只是一扇時開時關的窗戶，房間裡有什麼，還是身處其中的人最清楚。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請告訴我，布朗陶夫人，您是否厭倦了這片土地上無休止且毫無意義的族群矛盾？", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或者說……您是否期待，由自己來引領一個全新的謝拉格？", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#2$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#4$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了，就到這裡吧。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "感謝您今晚撥冗前來，我已經完全理解你們的提議了——我也有話請您轉告你們的公爵大人。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#5$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她還不夠瞭解謝拉格，但我發自內心地希望她瞭解。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#5$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "明白了，布朗陶夫人。雖然很遺憾，不過在這些政治問題解決之前，我們之間的商務合作恐怕需要暫緩了。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過也無妨，對於您這位重要的合作夥伴，我們還是有著充足的耐心的。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們永遠期待您的回覆。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g10_manorhouse", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$normal_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper2"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "親愛的恩希亞，見字如晤。", "x": 180.0, "y": 170.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n你看到這封信的時候，應該已經知道了我的決定。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n不用擔心，就當作姐姐只是出一趟遠門，過不了多久就會回來了。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "答應帶你去蔓珠院的廚房偷吃起司火鍋的計劃，可能又要延遲了，不過等我回來的時候，我一定兌現承諾，我保證。", "x": 180.0, "y": 170.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n也不用替恩希歐迪斯擔心，他有自己的安排，只是這段時間可能會格外繁忙一點，就要拜託你一個人看家啦。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n最近發生了許多事，你一定要保護好自己，出門時一定要小心謹慎一點。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "我要出發了，要是回來的時候，能看到也和往常一樣開心的你就再好不過了。", "x": 180.0, "y": 170.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n我會為你們向耶拉岡德祈福的。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "另外，要記得按時去羅德島複查，遵守醫囑，爬山前要穿好護具。", "x": 180.0, "y": 170.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_267_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是恩雅的信嗎？", "name": "切斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_267_1#1$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#7$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "每次都是這樣。", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#7$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老哥也是，家裡本來就冷冷清清的，我這趟旅行回來後，家裡更是好像沒有這個人一樣。", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#7$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_267_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "非常時期，他們也一定在為保護謝拉格竭盡全力。", "name": "切斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_267_1#7$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩希亞，我們能做的也只有相信他們，支持他們……", "name": "切斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_267_1#7$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道……我就是有點生氣。", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#7$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們總是當我還是個小孩子，什麼都不讓我知道，最後又害我白擔心。", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#7$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也想幫他們出份力啊……", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#7$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_282_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩希亞小姐、切斯特老爺……", "name": "希瓦艾什家傭人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_282_1#1$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩希歐迪斯老爺不在嗎……？", "name": "希瓦艾什家傭人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_282_1#1$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老哥這個時間點已經去公司了吧，怎麼了？", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_282_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蔓珠院使者來訪，說今天要和佩爾羅契家進行礦產管理切割的會議，他們請老爺提前送交相關文件。", "name": "希瓦艾什家傭人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_282_1#1$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_267_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_scroll", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "會議文件的確在我這裡……可是提前送交？這是臨時通知？", "name": "切斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_267_1#5$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_282_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "詳細情況，那位使者也沒有說明……", "name": "希瓦艾什家傭人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_282_1#1$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_267_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧，來人備車，我去一趟。", "name": "切斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_267_1#1$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_openftstprun", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "nrun"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "nrun", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "話音剛落，恩希亞已經搶過文件一溜煙地奔出門外。"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "切斯特叔叔，你在家休息吧，我去幫老哥辦這件事情，放心吧！", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#1$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_267_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩希亞……！快點回來！", "name": "切斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_267_1#4$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老爺叮囑過，不讓您隨意出門的！", "name": "切斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_267_1#4$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒關係啦！肯定是老哥糊里糊塗忘了帶東西，等一下我還要好好嘲笑他！", "name": "恩希亞"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "開車開車！", "name": "恩希亞"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$sportscarstart", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_267_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這怎麼搞的……", "name": "切斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_267_1#5$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是先通知老爺吧……", "name": "切斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_267_1#5$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "40_g2_glacier", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 0.01, "fillto": 0.07, "fadetime": 0.1}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 4.0, "fillfrom": 0.01, "fillto": 0.07, "fadetime": 0.1}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_driveincar", "volume": 0.0, "channel": "car", "loop": "true"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.8, "channel": "car", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "清晨，一輛棕色的車行駛在通往蔓珠院的山路，坐在後座的阿克托斯搥了搥自己的脖頸。"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵——欠。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#2$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大清早地叫我去開會，礦區管理切割的事情有這麼著急嗎？", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_260_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽說這段時間，恩希歐迪斯大人經常在喀蘭貿易忙通宵，早上會談也符合他近期的作息。", "name": "古羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_260_1#1$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼——", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說到底，該聊的之前也聊得差不多了，也就是等希瓦艾什那邊整理好文件，我再確認簽名。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "古羅，把上次的會談記錄拿出來，我再看一遍。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_260_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是，老爺。", "name": "古羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_260_1#1$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "副駕駛座位上的古羅從儲物箱抽出一疊文件，正要回頭遞給阿克托斯，突然車身一震。"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "car", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$drift", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$plot_intro", "key": "$plot_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "該死！怎麼回事？", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是、是、是落石！差點就被砸中了！", "name": "佩爾羅契司機"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_260_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "落石？這裡怎麼會有落石？", "name": "古羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_260_1#7$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_erthshkng", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "e"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_hgldshcrrig", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_vallyrck", "volume": 1.0, "delay": 0.3}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "話音剛落，車身又一次劇烈震動，掉落的碎石重重砸向後車廂。"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_260_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老爺！車裡不安全，前面的路都被石頭堵死了，我們應該馬上下車！", "name": "古羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_260_1#6$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "*謝拉格俚語*！", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#8$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "e", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cardoorc", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$smallearthquake", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 3.0, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 12.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三人棄車，往靠近山壁的一側奔去，然而碎石的數量令他們束手無策。"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_260_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老爺小心——", "name": "古羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_260_1#6$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_runstop", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovementsp", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown2", "volume": 1.0, "delay": 0.3}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "碎石直衝阿克托斯而來，古羅奮力將阿克托斯推開，碎石的邊緣擊中他的額頭，頓時血流如注，巨大的身軀重重倒在地上。"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "被推倒在地的阿克托斯手腳並用地爬向古羅，他拉住古羅的手用盡全身力氣將他拖向山壁旁，路面上留下了一條長長的血跡。"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "石塊隨之落下，幾乎快將血跡蓋過。"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "古羅，古羅！", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#8$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g12_mountpath", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_enginerun", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "鐧"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "晨霧散去，引擎的轟鳴打破了雪山的寧靜，然而這份寂靜並非是鐧此刻的期待。"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鐧將摩托車的油門催到底，山道兩側的景象在她的眼眸上飛速交替，卻始終沒有她在尋找的身影。"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "山道上兩道車轍還清晰可見，她追蹤的人應該剛離開不久。"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_hgateburst", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在前面——！", "name": "鐧"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$drift", "volume": 0.7, "delay": 0.2}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鐧翻身下車，轉過這處山路彎道——"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g12_mountpath", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_churchfire", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "b"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.3, "channel": "b", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#6$1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#6$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "前方不遠處，兩輛車橫撞在一起，燃起熊熊火焰，劇烈的濃煙伴隨著焦臭向外擴散。"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_jandrg"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_brnchflsnw", "delay": 0.6}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "b", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鐧立即拔出了腰間的武器，長鐧揚起的風雪熄滅了火勢——她看到了熟悉的希瓦艾什家的座車。"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "長鐧輕鬆地劃開了車門，鐧沒有看到她最害怕的景象，車內空無一人。"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_vallyrck", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“砰砰”，山崖處傳來石頭碰撞的聲響。"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g12_mountpath", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "style": "slider", "inverse": "true", "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#6$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鐧立刻朝著聲響的源頭向下望去——儘管臉頰上滿是塵灰，但鐧認出了這就是她要尋找的人。"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鐧姐！", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#6$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#6$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#6$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "用鉤爪固定在山岩上的恩希亞，仰頭望向鐧，一時不知做出什麼表情才能緩解此時的尷尬。"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，我搞砸了，嘿嘿……", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#6$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g1_snowyforest", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$monastery_sad_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowstormlp", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "wind"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.7, "channel": "wind", "fadetime": 4.0}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_blizzard", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#10$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……“祂的國不為來日而許諾。”", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#10$1"}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“也不為昨日而建造。”", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#10$1"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“謹記行走之人最親近祂。”", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#10$1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“祂的恩典，時刻在旅者的腳下。”", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#10$1"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1"}, {"id": 355, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雪花沾黏在白色毛領上，孤獨的旅人拉了拉帽兜，迎著穿林而過的寒風，向山上前行。"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斗篷緊裹著身軀，樹林中掉落的枝條混合著積雪，牽絆著恩雅的腳步。"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "修士們常說，雪虐風饕是耶拉岡德考驗信眾的方式，但恩雅知道，“祂”絕不會如此折磨自己。"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雅兒……", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#12$1"}, {"id": 362, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幸運的是，森林尚有聖女的喘息之所。她看見林中深處升起篝火的煙霧，似乎有個可以落足休息的地方。"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩雅走了過去，尚未熄滅的火焰帶來難得的暖意，她不由得湊到篝火旁，伸出雙手。"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "懸掛的獸皮說明這裡是一處獵人的營地，灌木環繞，孤零零的木屋裡也不見人影。"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_grass", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_bowstring_tightened", "volume": 0.3, "delay": 0.8}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不遠處的灌木搖動，發出窸窸窣窣的微響，金屬箭頭從葉片中伸出，往篝火那邊瞄準——"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼人？", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#6$1"}, {"id": 375, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$darkness_03_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_bowstring_rebound", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 12.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 0.2, "b": 0.2, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.4, "r": 1.0, "g": 0.2, "b": 0.2, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 0.2, "b": 0.2, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩雅迅速轉身，疾速飛來的箭矢還是正中她的右腿，鮮血在厚厚的衣裝上暈染一片。"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_283_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7, "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她下意識地舉起搖鈴，劇烈的疼痛讓她站立不穩。襲擊者卻已走出灌木叢，他搭上的第二支箭，正好瞄準了聖女的心臟。"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_slbellbtl", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_arrowshot", "delay": 0.3}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_arrowtarget", "volume": 0.6, "delay": 0.6}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowbodyfall", "volume": 1.0, "delay": 1.0}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗖——"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鈴聲隨之響動，風雪淹沒了倒地的襲擊者，然而雪地漸漸滲出紅色，這絕不是聖鈴的能力。"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩雅細看才發覺，伏擊者的咽喉上插著一支短箭。"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-100,0", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovementsp", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.7, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "突然，粗糙有力的小手握住了恩雅的臂膀，將她狠狠拉向一邊。"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_arrow"}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowbodyfall", "volume": 1.0, "delay": 0.5}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowcrwdmarch", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_284_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7, "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_284_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7, "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "細微的箭矢破空聲響起，遠處的新襲擊者應聲而倒，但他們的同黨正接連從森林的偽裝中現身。"}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "*謝拉格俚語*，哪來的土匪，竟然敢趁我不在，用我的營地幹謀財害命的事！", "name": "小獵手"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#6$2", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一位獵手打扮的少女，舉著對她的體型而言顯得有些龐大的重弩，混雜著藥草與雲獸的氣味，跨步擋在了恩雅身前。"}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#8$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還傻傻站著幹嘛？！", "name": "小獵手"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#8$2"}, {"id": 428, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#5$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "小獵手"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#5$2"}, {"id": 430, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是希瓦艾什的人……你怎麼會在這裡？", "name": "小獵手"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#5$2"}, {"id": 431, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#8$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……算了，先跟緊我！", "name": "小獵手"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#8$2"}, {"id": 433, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "wind", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 435, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 437, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}